com.iciql.util

Class IciqlLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iciql.util.IciqlLogger

  • public class IciqlLogger
extends java.lang.Object
    Utility class to optionally log generated statements to IciqlListeners.
    Statement logging is disabled by default.

    This class also tracks the counts for generated statements by major type.
